##  6 Hyper        Capp Cont AF                 NA <NA>         <NA>           
##  7 Hyper        Capp Cont CHD                NA <NA>         <NA>           
##  8 Hyper        Capp Cont CHD                NA <NA>         <NA>           
##  9 Hyper        Capp Cont CHD                NA <NA>         <NA>           
## 10 Hyper        Capp Cont CHD                NA <NA>         <NA>           
## #  with 2,558 more rows, and 24 more variables: `abstract score` <chr>,
## #   ID <int>, system <chr>, cohort <chr>, low_selected <lgl>,
## #   high_selected <lgl>, Thyroid_test <chr>, N <dbl>, method <chr>, Sig <chr>,
## #   Sophistication <chr>, cov <chr>, total <chr>, inferred <lgl>, pv <dbl>,
## #   bounded <lgl>, OR <dbl>, ORCI <chr>, count <chr>, countCI <chr>,
## #   Thyroid_test_4 <chr>, high_low <chr>, n_cov <chr>, N_bin <fct>
overall_ci  <- 
  TSH_long %>% 
  filter(!is.na(Sig)) %>% 
  group_by(Thyroid_test) %>% 
  summarise(
    n_sig = sum(Sig == "Y"), 
    N = n(), 
    p = n_sig / N,
    lwr = p - 1.96 * sqrt(p * (1 - p) / N),
    upr = p + 1.96 * sqrt(p * (1 - p) / N)
  )
overall_ci
## # A tibble: 3 x 6
##   Thyroid_test n_sig     N     p   lwr   upr
##   <chr>        <int> <int> <dbl> <dbl> <dbl>
## 1 FT4            411   856 0.480 0.447 0.514
## 2 T3             139   297 0.468 0.411 0.525
## 3 TSH            184   856 0.215 0.187 0.242
ggplot(overall_ci, aes( Thyroid_test, p, col = Thyroid_test)) + 
  geom_point() + 
  geom_errorbar(aes(ymin = lwr, ymax = upr), width = 0.1) + 
  theme(legend.position = "none") + 
  labs(y = "Proportion")
